Class SongList

java.lang.Object
SongList
public class SongList
extends java.lang.Object
SongList Class
Since:
November 2020 Simple SongList object The SongList is the full list of songs from which a PlayList may be selected.
Author:
Suzy Atfield-Cutts

    Constructors 
    Constructor Description
    SongList()
